high_descs: Turn left. Continue down the corridor to the dresser. Turn right, then left and left again to be in front of the dresser.
Grab the fork.
Turn left. Then to the right and then to the left. To the right, enter the corridor. Enter the sink.
Place the fork in the sink, next to the left faucet.
Return to the room. Stand in front of the bed.
Grab the fork.
Go back to the sink in the bathroom.
Place the fork on the right side of the other fork in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Find two Forks and place them next to a Sink faucet.

high_descs: walk straight towards the dresser
pick up the fork from the dresser
turn left and then right towards the sink
place the fork in the sink
turn left towards the bed
pick up the fork from the bed
turn back and then left towards the sink
place the fork in the sink
anns.task_desc: place the forks in the sink

high_descs: Go straight and near to the dresser.
Pick up the fork from the wooden table.
Go straight turn right and turn right near to the sink.
Put the fork into the sink.
Walk back and near to the bed.
Pick up the fork from the bed.
Turn around walk back and near to the sink.
Keep the fork on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Pick the fork from the wooden table and keep it on the sink.
